  "local_port": 48966,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What is the best and most economic perfume for men in India?",
  "response": "Choosing the best and most economical perfume for men in India involves balancing quality, longevity, fragrance profile, and price. Here are some top recommendations that offer great value without breaking the bank:\n\n### 1. **Park Avenue Fair Lady Perfume**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9300 - \u20b9600\n- **Notes:** A sophisticated blend of woody and oriental notes.\n- **Pros:** Long-lasting, suitable for daily wear, widely available.\n- **Cons:** Scent may be strong for some preferences.\n\n### 2. **Engage Hombre Perfume**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9200 - \u20b9500\n- **Notes:** Fresh, aromatic fragrance with citrus and woody undertones.\n- **Pros:** Affordable, good longevity, versatile for both casual and formal settings.\n- **Cons:** May not have as complex a scent as higher-end options.\n\n### 3. **Fogg Body Spray**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9150 - \u20b9300\n- **Notes:** Crisp and fresh with citrus and floral hints.\n- **Pros:** Extremely budget-friendly, easily accessible in most stores, good for layering.\n- **Cons:** May require reapplication throughout the day.\n\n### 4. **Denver Hamilton Classic**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9250 - \u20b9600\n- **Notes:** Spicy and woody notes with a hint of sweetness.\n- **Pros:** Pleasant and mature scent, decent longevity, suitable for evening wear.\n- **Cons:** Limited availability outside major cities.\n\n### 5. **Ustraa Deodorant Body Spray**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9200 - \u20b9500\n- **Notes:** Herbal and fresh fragrance with a masculine edge.\n- **Pros:** Natural ingredients, good for sensitive skin, stylish packaging.\n- **Cons:** Body spray consistency may not last as long as traditional perfumes.\n\n### 6. **Jaguar Classic Black**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b91,500 - \u20b92,500\n- **Notes:** A blend of spicy, woody, and warm notes.\n- **Pros:** High-quality scent, excellent longevity, suitable for special occasions.\n- **Cons:** Slightly higher in price compared to other economical options, but offers better quality.\n\n### 7. **Wild Stone Code**\n- **Price Range:** \u20b9250 - \u20b9600\n- **Notes:** Woody and spicy with a fresh opening.\n- **Pros:** Popular among young men, good for daily use, affordable.\n- **Cons:** May not stand out for those preferring unique or niche fragrances.\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Perfume:**\n\n1. **Test Before Buying:** Whenever possible, sample the fragrance on your skin to ensure it complements your body chemistry.\n2. **Consider Longevity:** If you need a long-lasting scent, opt for eau de parfum (EDP) over eau de toilette (EDT) as they generally last longer.\n3. **Season and Occasion:** Lighter, fresher scents are ideal for daytime and warmer months, while deeper, spicier fragrances work well for evenings and colder seasons.\n4. **Check Reviews:** Online reviews and ratings can provide insights into the perfume\u2019s performance and popularity.\n\n### **Conclusion**\n\nFor the best balance of quality and affordability in India, **Engage Hombre Perfume** and **Wild Stone Code** are excellent choices for everyday use, offering pleasant scents and good longevity without a hefty price tag. If you're looking for something slightly more premium while still being economical, **Jaguar Classic Black** provides a sophisticated fragrance that lasts longer, making it suitable for various occasions.\n\nUltimately, the \"best\" perfume is subjective and depends on personal preference, so it's advisable to try a few options to see which one aligns best with your style and scent preferences.",
